_sText:
A small closed off indoors arena


Background:
A map set in a small styled arena with small slits of space between you and your opponent. The map allows for bouncing of grenades and doors that later break once time limit has reached.

Support:
Cubemaps, Grenade_spawners, Overtime ("Guns Spawn"), 48 Spawnpoints

ChangeLog:
  • [ADDED] Glass in opening between steel doors,
  • [ADDED] Custom Texture,
  • [ADDED] New Sound for overtime
